<h2 align="center">Art Residency „Tuta“</h2><div>Residency is a comfortable space located in the historic house&nbsp;renovated&nbsp;by the National Trust of Georgia and ICOMOS Georgia. It's resident can become any person who wishes to be in solitude to work on his/her project, or seeks for inspiration to realize new idea.</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://www.nationaltrustofgeorgia.org.ge/img/pages/im_1738066571746850.png"></div><div>Building is situated in the historic Kbode neighborhood, Avlabari. Rooms for the resident are available in the mansard with a private entrance, WC and balcony.<br><br><div><img src="https://a0.muscache.com/im/pictures/miso/Hosting-755538670030162413/original/09be86d3-78a4-44e9-bc40-777be5592b46.jpeg?im_w=720&amp;im_format=avif" alt="Listing image 6"><br>Staircase from the courtyard balcony</div><div><img src="https://a0.muscache.com/im/pictures/miso/Hosting-755538670030162413/original/7d01e825-6eea-4c90-86d6-10cb9704b81f.jpeg?im_w=720&amp;im_format=avif" alt="Listing image 1"></div><div>Bedroom</div><div><img src="https://a0.muscache.com/im/pictures/miso/Hosting-755538670030162413/original/dbf91586-7308-45cc-83d1-9d8d3591fbed.jpeg?im_w=720&amp;im_format=avif" alt="Listing image 3"></div><div>WC<img src="https://a0.muscache.com/im/pictures/miso/Hosting-755538670030162413/original/3df06608-6b3d-4c71-a66e-5263370dece4.jpeg?im_w=720&amp;im_format=avif" alt="Listing image 5"></div><div>View from the courtyard balcony</div><div><img src="https://a0.muscache.com/im/pictures/miso/Hosting-755538670030162413/original/192e7814-bd43-4bc8-b3d5-210c8fbb9fc0.jpeg?im_w=720&amp;im_format=avif" alt="Listing image 7"></div><div>View from the street faced balcony<br><br></div>If you are interested to book the stay please contact us on email (indicate in the title Residency "Tuta") or call on the number indicated in the contact.</div>